Weclome To EIES

The most active student society of the Department of Electrical And Information Engineering of the Faculty of Engineering, University of Ruhuna provides DEIE students the chance to grow their technical and soft skills via many events

Head Of Department
Dr Eranda Jayatunga


Senior Lecturer MEng (AIT, Thailand) BScEng (Hons) (Peradeniya)

Message From Head Of Department

Welcome to the Electrical and Information Engineering Society (EIES) of the Department of Electrical and Information Engineering. Although the department has many societies, this is the main forum accustomed to upgrading student’s life in the department by allowing them to improve not only academic and technical skills but also their leadership interpersonal and professional qualities. It has the responsibility of organizing workshops in collaboration with Alumni Association of Ruhuna Electrical and Information Engineering (AAREIE) and conducting annual calendar events such as XbotiX robotics competition, HackDoze, Career Fair, etc. This website provides an overview of student activities inherent to EIES.
